        <body>
            <div1 n="2" rendition="#manuscript">
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">The president is gone.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">And the vice president is gone too.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">We created a world where</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper"> we didn't need these false idols.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="3" rendition="#manuscript">
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">The priest is gone. The missonaries are all gone
                    too.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">We didn't need them telling us what to do.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">We decided to some thinking for ourselves.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">So now</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">The police are gone,</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">The sherrifs and deputies and hey the criminals are
                    all gone too.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">Theres no jails and no prisons, no heartless</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">warehouses full of people, living breathing.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">We didn't want those things anymore. So we</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">Got rid of all our bosses, we all quit our
                    "jobs"</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">and realized we could actually find our
                    purpose...</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="4" rendition="#manuscript">
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper">We got rid of the Landlords ... it</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper">wasn't there land to "lord" anyway ...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper">and we got rid of renters too.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper">Now were all just livers... livers ?</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper">Haha ... I mean were all people who get to be
                    alive,</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper">People who get to experience our world</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper">and not just fight to survive it.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="5" rendition="#manuscript">
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper">So we got rid of the corporations. That's right.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink pink_paper"> Now the CEOs are gone and the shareholders and
                    investors and even the consumers are gone too.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">We got rid of them when</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">They were treating the rest of the world like a
                    game ...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">They played by unfair rules...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">So we burned the Rulebook</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">And the game board, all the cards and the dice,</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">and we got rid of the markets and the money</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">we started valuing people ...animals ...plants ...
                    the world ...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">For what they are :</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">Gifts ... Blessigngs ... not from any of us ... to
                    all of us ...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">Gifts.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="6" rendition="#manuscript">
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">So we got rid of the food prices and the "cost" of
                    healthcare and</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">decided to live in abundance. We stopped putting a
                    price tag on life.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">So we got rid of the rich. And we got rid of the
                    poor. We decided that we all could do more...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">We got rid of the borders and walls... The binary
                    structures that kept us apart...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">We realized how fragile they were, how easily they
                    cdould crumble.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">They didn't stand a chance against the power we had
                    ...</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">That we still have.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">The power of love ... creativity ...solidarity</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_paper">We nenver once surrendered.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="7" rendition="#manuscript">
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">So now the hatred is gone. The silence and shame
                    too.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">We got rid of them; we loved to hard !</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">In the best way possible. We embodied our
                    truths.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">We didn't let lies stop us. So we got rid of the
                    mass media and legislators are all gone too !</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">We got rid of the teachers, there are no more of
                    them and we got rid of the students too.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">We realized we have lots more fun when we all
                    become learners, creators, participants in our reality and not mere predefined
                    roles.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">And we were so successful ! We still are.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="8" rendition="#manuscript">
                <p rend="purple_ink white_tissue">And now the violence is all gone,</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_tissue">and the tanks and guns are gone too.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_tissue">The gas is gone, the bombs, the chemicals they
                    dumped into the earth our home.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_tissue">They are all gone.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_tissue">We got rid of them !</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_tissue">Chose life,</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink white_tissue">Chose love, chose connection instead of fear.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="9" rendition="#manuscript">
                <p rend="purple_ink, blue surgical mask">We chose each other.And we still do. That's
                    how we made it so far.</p>
            </div1>
            <div1 n="10" rendition="#manuscript">
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">But we looked beyond ourselves too and we chose
                    the world, again as it is, gifts, glorious and abundant and we realized we had
                    so much we were missing.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">So we don't have the scarcity the fear and
                    coercion any more.</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">No more extraction and expansion and exploitation
                    - that's all gone. We embraced cycles and transitions, trangressions,
                    transformations,</p>
                <p rend="purple_ink yellow_paper">We got rid of control and welcomed in community.
                    And we thrive, and we thrive, and we thrive, and we thrive.</p>
            </div1>
        </body>
